room_title: Escape room "Houdini's Challenge" by Paradox Challenge Rooms in Tupelo
review: Even though we didn't make it out, we still had lots of fun! There was only 3 of us doing the Houdini challenge. Not only did the story and the theme went with the puzzles well, our game master was awesome and always in character (Jeremy). Definitely will be back.
